AND WE GET DISCOURAGED.

1200
01:17:26,124 --> 01:17:30,335
BUT I DO BELIEVE
THAT WITH FAMILY

1201
01:17:30,369 --> 01:17:35,789
WE HAVE THE CAPACITY
TO FORGIVE AND BE FORGIVEN

1202
01:17:35,823 --> 01:17:37,825
AS IN NO OTHER PLACE
IN LIFE.

1203
01:17:45,315 --> 01:17:51,183
TIME AND MEMORY
ARE SO FLEETING.

1204
01:17:51,218 --> 01:17:56,119
WE MUST SAVOR EVERY MOMENT

1205
01:17:56,154 --> 01:17:58,121
BECAUSE IT COULD JUST
SLIP AWAY

1206
01:17:58,156 --> 01:18:01,918
WITHOUT OUR EVER NOTICING IT.

1207
01:18:01,952 --> 01:18:05,128
HERE'S TO MY FAMILY.

1208
01:18:10,858 --> 01:18:12,757
- HERE'S TO YOU, MAMA.

