1233
01:19:30,386 --> 01:19:34,148
- YEAH. IT'S A GOOD DAY FOR HER.- HMM.

1234
01:19:34,183 --> 01:19:37,427
- YOU KNOW, I NEVER THOUGHT
I'D SAY THIS,

1235
01:19:37,462 --> 01:19:40,914
BUT I'M REALLY GLAD
I CAME HOME.

1236
01:19:40,948 --> 01:19:42,260
- GOOD.

1237
01:19:42,294 --> 01:19:44,987
